name: Sevens Road Witch (Rush)
text:
[REQUIREMENT] Send 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard.
[EFFECT] Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher, DARK Attribute, Spellcaster Type monster from your hand, face-up to your field. If you Special Summoned "Sevens Road Magician" by this effect, this card gains 400 ATK until the end of this turn.
